# Folder Structure

## Layout

```
src/
├── app/                    # App shell, router, providers, lazy-pages
├── features/<kebab-name>/  # One folder per module (19 total)
│   ├── components/
│   ├── hooks/
│   ├── api/
│   ├── types/
│   └── index.ts            # Barrel — public API only
├── shared/
│   ├── components/         # ui/, layout/, data-table/, charts/, etc.
│   ├── hooks/
│   ├── lib/                # axios, query-client, utils, merchant-store, etc.
│   ├── config/             # env, routes, permissions, feature-flags
│   └── types/
├── locales/en/ + locales/ml/   # i18n namespace JSON per feature + common
├── styles/globals.css      # Tailwind v4 + shadcn theme tokens
└── assets/
```

## Rules

- **Always** create new features under `src/features/<kebab-name>/` with all five subfolders + `index.ts`
- **Never** dump feature-specific code into `shared/` unless genuinely cross-feature (layout, DataTable wrapper, shadcn ui)
- shadcn components live at `src/shared/components/ui/` — not `src/components/ui/`
- Barrel `index.ts` re-exports **public API only** (page components, hooks consumed by other features) — not every internal file
- **Never** add new top-level `src/` folders without explicit user confirmation — ask first
- App wiring stays in `src/app/` (`router.tsx`, `lazy-pages.tsx`, `providers.tsx`)
